      <title>安巴尼合并谈判中迪士尼印度部门估值减半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/disney-s-india-unit-valuation-halves-in-ambani-merger-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华特迪士尼公司印度部门的估值还不到其与印度亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼媒体业务合并时所希望的一半，这反映出全球媒体巨头在全球增长最快的娱乐市场之一所面临的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/disney-s-india-unit-valuation-halves-in-ambani-merger-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:17:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信贷交易员正在利用违约掉期来对冲利率押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/credit-traders-are-using-default-swaps-to-hedge-their-bets-on-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[野村资产管理公司(Nomura Asset Management)的理查德·霍奇斯(Richard Hodges)年初购买了信用违约掉期产品，担心降息押注变得过于激进。当保护成本增加时，他减少了对冲，现在准备再次介入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/credit-traders-are-using-default-swaps-to-hedge-their-bets-on-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:05:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国山东省地方政府融资平台延长债务偿还期限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/lgfv-in-china-s-shandong-province-extends-debt-payment-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国山东省的一家地方政府融资平台与债权人达成协议，部分偿还其4.79亿元人民币（合6680万美元）的非债券债务，并延长了几乎全部的还款期限，凸显了尽管有政府支持，该行业仍面临流动性挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/lgfv-in-china-s-shandong-province-extends-debt-payment-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东广播公司 MBC 是全球表现最佳的 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/middle-eastern-broadcaster-is-world-s-best-performing-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家中东广播公司的股价上涨了两倍多，使其成为今年全球表现最好的上市公司，突显了这个为数不多的繁忙首次公开募股市场之一的持续强势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/middle-eastern-broadcaster-is-world-s-best-performing-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 10:02:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中泰三月起签署互免签证协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/china-thailand-to-sign-pact-on-visa-free-travel-starting-march</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国和泰国将于 3 月 1 日签署协议，免除两国旅客签证要求，外交部长王毅将于本周访问这个东南亚邻国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/china-thailand-to-sign-pact-on-visa-free-travel-starting-march</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:58:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利央行拒绝贷款利率计划，提振福林</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/hungarian-central-bank-rejects-loan-rate-plan-boosting-forint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利央行对政府工作文件提出的银行贷款新参考利率进行了回击，称这将增加不确定性、造成利益冲突并损害该国的风险认知。福林兑欧元汇率上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/hungarian-central-bank-rejects-loan-rate-plan-boosting-forint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德李嘉诚认为通货紧缩将推动市场和风险情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-25/blackrock-s-li-immaculate-disinflation-to-drive-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球首席投资策略师李伟表示：“了解这种完美通货紧缩的说法能持续多久、持续多久，可能会成为今年市场和风险情绪的驱动力。” （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-25/blackrock-s-li-immaculate-disinflation-to-drive-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:53:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯天然气出口因对华出口量增加而复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/russia-sees-its-natural-gas-exports-recovering-on-higher-shipments-to-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯预计今年其管道天然气出口将恢复近五分之一，部分抵消大部分欧洲客户因对中国发货量增加而造成的损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-25/russia-sees-its-natural-gas-exports-recovering-on-higher-shipments-to-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jan 2024 09:52:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉业绩缓和乐观情绪，股市暂停：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于特斯拉公司令人失望的业绩削弱了近期涨势，全球股市暂停，投资者为欧洲央行会议和美国经济增长数据做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 22:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
